{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, existing research on nutrition evaluation has ignored the impact of prompt engineering techniques 20, 24, 29.",
    "They have been limited to zero-shot prompting methods with either no instructions or fixed instructions.",
    "The zero-shot prompting instructs LLMs to perform specific tasks without providing any prior examples.",
    "This technique is straightforward and is widely used.",
    "However, it might be insufficient for LLM response generation if problem-solving or contextual information is needed."
  ]
}